(226, 1, '2015-06-06 23:16:24', '2015-06-06 17:46:24', '&nbsp;\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Isn''t it a funny thing?</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">What you think you see are words </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">But rather images aligning </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">With perfect lines and curves </span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Why are birth and death called so? </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Why is a cow''s moo; a moo?</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">The shirt you wear, your mother''s hair </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">A baby''s eyes and the sky; both a calming blue. </span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">We can''t live without these little puzzles</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">When linked, they provide clues </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">To thoughts, to life and to victorious endeavours </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">To literature, conversation, song... they''re yours to choose</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Words contain questions and answers </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">They last thoughout the ages </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">My grandfather''s favourite fairytale </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Or the science gathered among the pages </span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">And these words bring people together </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Language unites and sets us free </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">But it is same words that bind us </span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 32px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">As when two different cultures meet. </span></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Story of Words', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '222-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-06 23:16:24', '2015-06-06 17:46:24', '', 222, 'http://blog.thebookhub.in/222-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
